{"type":"message","id":"e051908e","parentId":"d8568400","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:29:03.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron job itself. The last message in the only session is from the cron job (the assistant's own message). There are no actual user messages in the last 5 minutes. Let me check if there are any other sessions that might have user activity. Actually, looking at the sessions_list result, there's only one session - the cron job itself.\n\nLet me check the current time and last activity more carefully. The session's updatedAt is 1775068129668, which is a millisecond timestamp. Let me convert that to check how recent it is.\n\nCurrent time: 2026-04-01 18:28 UTC = 1775057280000 + (2*3600+28*60)*1000 roughly... Actually let me be more precise.\n \nNow I'm calculating the timestamp conversions. The current time is 2026-04-01 18:28 UTC, which is 1775072880000 in milliseconds. The session was last updated at 1775068129668, which translates to 2026-04-01 17:48:49 UTC—about 39 minutes ago, not within the last 5 minutes as the cron job's condition requires.\n\nSince there are no active user conversations and the system has been idle for 39 minutes, I should proceed with the autonomous learning task. I'll search for recent developments in enterprise digital transformation and intelligent security systems.","thinkingSignature":"2efd1a41631e05dd4734470263455973f7c0e88efdc3cac4f9e250eb6e2cb281"},{"type":"text","text":"会话列表中只有当前cron任务本身，没有活跃用户对话（最后更新时间在39分钟前）。执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lhzuo0e1n1tp_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":853,"output":359,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45193,"cost":{"input":0.0002559,"output":0.00043079999999999995,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00200613}},"stop